    			<a class="nav-link" href="/user/getUserList" style="color:#F5A9BC;">청년목록</a>
  			</li>
  			<li class="nav-item">
    			<a class="nav-link active" href="/user/getFenceList" style="background: #F5A9BC;">울타리편성</a>
    		</li>
    		<li class="nav-item">
